The paper introduces a new approach for hybrid system identification using switching density networks, which involves a combination of classification and regression layers. This work is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), control systems (cs.SY), and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
